    <description>
        <short>
            <en>Automatically generates unique IDs for GLPI assets based on type, group, and sequence.</en>
        </short>
        <long>
            <en>
The **ID Generator** plugin for GLPI automatically assigns unique identifiers to assets such as Computers, Monitors, Printers, Phones, and more. The ID format follows a `TYPE-GRP-NUM` structure (e.g., `PC-IT-001` for a Computer in the IT group). IDs are generated based on the asset type, technical group, and an incremental number. The ID remains fixed after creation unless the technical group changes, ensuring consistent asset tracking. Supports a wide range of asset types, including peripherals like headsets, chargers, and docking stations.
            </en>
        </long>
    </description>
